    {
      "id": "PopularPost282680",
      "post_content": "[Grizzly Bears](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Grizzly Bears) and [Centaur Courser](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Centaur Courser) are weak creatures, giving each color these weak cards wont ruin the game, because they wont get played regardless.   \n  \nAll it will do is increase the power level of budget players decks, and their is nothing wrong with that. Weak cards dont define formats, strong cards do. Heck even Urza and Mirrodin had its weak cards, but they didnt slow down the powerhouses that are legacy staples to this day, did they?  \n  \nYou could give green a common [watchwolf](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=watchwolf) for ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Green](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=G&type=symbol), and a 4/4 for ![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol)![Green](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=G&type=symbol). ",
      "posted_by": "TheWrathofShane",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost282680\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\"><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Grizzly Bears\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Grizzly Bears\">Grizzly Bears</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Centaur Courser\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Centaur Courser\">Centaur Courser</a> are weak creatures, giving each color these weak cards wont ruin the game, because they wont get played regardless. <br/><br/>All it will do is increase the power level of budget players decks, and their is nothing wrong with that. Weak cards dont define formats, strong cards do. Heck even Urza and Mirrodin had its weak cards, but they didnt slow down the powerhouses that are legacy staples to this day, did they?<br/><br/>You could give green a common <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"watchwolf\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=watchwolf\">watchwolf</a> for <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Green\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=G&amp;type=symbol\"/>, and a 4/4 for <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"2\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=2&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Green\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=G&amp;type=symbol\"/>. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '282680'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy34054\">TheWrathofShane</span>\r\n                                (11/23/2012 2:23:22 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
